                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 footer-col">
                    <div class="more-space h4">My projects</div>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled list-vertical">
                        <li class=""><a href="http://www.navihub.net/">Navihub</a> <small class="gray">&#8592; you are here</small></li>
                        <li class=""><a href="http://www.tomatoid.com/">Tomatoid</a></li>
                        <li class=""><a href="http://www.petrnagy.cz/#projects">Daily menu</a></li>
                        <li class=""><a href="http://www.petrnagy.cz/#projects">EventCal</a></li>
